{"tid":2182414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上水「和你Shop」兩未成年男生撤控守行為 惟多一名16歲女生被控","createTime":"2020-08-31T09:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T09:54:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e890679ab19b1e1096ba4863930384527df93ca1","tid":2182414,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/UCZU57Q67NCXRNB55KRYJKVETI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FUCZU57Q67NCXRNB55KRYJKVETI%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=f4008a95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FUCZU57Q67NCXRNB55KRYJKVETI%2F&h=eaa15259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/UCZU57Q67NCXRNB55KRYJKVETI/</a><br />\n<br />\n網民去年12月28日在上水發起「和你Shop」活動，抗議水貨客擾亂上水居民生活，大批警員闖進商場，拘捕多人。事後九人被控非法集結、襲警等罪，其中一名14歲女生早前獲准簽保守行為結案；餘下被告今再訊，再多兩名未成年學生獲撤銷控罪，准以2,000元簽保、守行為兩年結案。惟事件中再有一名16歲女學生被控，案件押後至10月29日再訊。"},{"pid":"c97c5b67329d0a1acfb788d9c29376b649f9907b","tid":2182414,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都好既，希望女手足大步攬過"},{"pid":"5082f44764606965bf9b02ada1eb3bd6b5a4738f","tid":2182414,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22048c4f7eab7213f0fe4757d02b1d9c13ccae3","tid":2182414,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3ae01a270b054c76eeab6b6fb0f416b9579762a3","tid":2182414,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"好消息來, 人無事就好"}]}